"🚀 **Exciting Opportunity: Lead II - Software Engineering** 🚀We are seeking a talented and experienced Senior Software Engineer with expertise in WPF (Windows Presentation Foundation), C#, and .NET development to join our team in Bayan Lepas! If you have 6 to 8 years of hands-on experience in developing desktop applications using WPF, along with a strong foundation in C# programming and the .NET framework, we want to hear from you! Key Responsibilities:• Design and develop user-friendly desktop applications using WPF, adhering to best practices and design patterns.• Implement responsive and visually appealing user interfaces that enhance user experience.• Utilize XAML for designing UI layouts and styles and integrate with backend logic seamlessly.• Write clean, efficient, and maintainable code in C# to implement application logic and business requirements.• Implement object-oriented design principles and patterns to ensure code scalability and reusability.• Debug and troubleshoot issues to ensure smooth application performance and functionality.• Leverage the .NET framework 4.7 and above to develop robust desktop applications, ensuring compatibility and interoperability.• Collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams including designers, testers, and product managers to deliver high-quality software solutions.• Mentor junior developers and contribute to knowledge sharing initiatives within the team.Qualifications:• Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or related field.• 5 to 8 years of professional experience in software development, with a focus on WPF, C#, and .NET technologies.• Strong proficiency in WPF development, including experience with MVVM (Model-View-ViewModel) architecture.• Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail.• Strong communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to collaborate effectively in a team environment.If you're ready to take your career to the next level, apply now!🔗 https://lnkd.in/gRNK2UhRhashtag#SoftwareEngineering hashtag#WPF hashtag#CSharp hashtag#DotNet hashtag#JobOpportunity hashtag#BayanLepas hashtag#Hiring hashtag#TechJobs"

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

Stop using 𝘋𝘢𝘵𝘦𝘛𝘪𝘮𝘦.𝘕𝘰𝘸 everywhere – It might break your app (and your brain)Many C# devs use DateTime.Now without a second thought.But here's the thing — DateTime.Now is local time, and that can be a trap in modern apps.𝐖𝐡𝐲 𝐢𝐭 𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐬:- Your app might run on multiple servers across time zones- Local time shifts with Daylight Saving Time- Comparing DateTime.Now values between systems? Risky business𝐔𝐬𝐞 𝐔𝐭𝐜𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐢𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐚𝐝:- Perfect for logging, storing timestamps, and calculating durationsI learned this the hard way while debugging user session expiries — all because DateTime.Now jumped an hour forward.𝘗𝘳𝘰 𝘛𝘪𝘱:Store in UTC, convert to local only when displaying to the user.How about you?Do you default to UtcNow in your code? Or do you still use Now in certain cases? Let’s discuss! 👇♻️ Repost and follow Umer Farooq for more .NET tips!hashtag#dotnet hashtag#csharp

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

Stop using 𝘋𝘢𝘵𝘦𝘛𝘪𝘮𝘦.𝘕𝘰𝘸 everywhere – It might break your app (and your brain)Many C# devs use DateTime.Now without a second thought.But here's the thing — DateTime.Now is local time, and that can be a trap in modern apps.𝐖𝐡𝐲 𝐢𝐭 𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐬:- Your app might run on multiple servers across time zones- Local time shifts with Daylight Saving Time- Comparing DateTime.Now values between systems? Risky business𝐔𝐬𝐞 𝐔𝐭𝐜𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐢𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐚𝐝:- Perfect for logging, storing timestamps, and calculating durationsI learned this the hard way while debugging user session expiries — all because DateTime.Now jumped an hour forward.𝘗𝘳𝘰 𝘛𝘪𝘱:Store in UTC, convert to local only when displaying to the user.How about you?Do you default to UtcNow in your code? Or do you still use Now in certain cases? Let’s discuss! 👇♻️ Repost and follow Umer Farooq for more .NET tips!hashtag#dotnet hashtag#csharp

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

Stop using 𝘋𝘢𝘵𝘦𝘛𝘪𝘮𝘦.𝘕𝘰𝘸 everywhere – It might break your app (and your brain)Many C# devs use DateTime.Now without a second thought.But here's the thing — DateTime.Now is local time, and that can be a trap in modern apps.𝐖𝐡𝐲 𝐢𝐭 𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐬:- Your app might run on multiple servers across time zones- Local time shifts with Daylight Saving Time- Comparing DateTime.Now values between systems? Risky business𝐔𝐬𝐞 𝐔𝐭𝐜𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐢𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐚𝐝:- Perfect for logging, storing timestamps, and calculating durationsI learned this the hard way while debugging user session expiries — all because DateTime.Now jumped an hour forward.𝘗𝘳𝘰 𝘛𝘪𝘱:Store in UTC, convert to local only when displaying to the user.How about you?Do you default to UtcNow in your code? Or do you still use Now in certain cases? Let’s discuss! 👇♻️ Repost and follow Umer Farooq for more .NET tips!hashtag#dotnet hashtag#csharp

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

Stop using 𝘋𝘢𝘵𝘦𝘛𝘪𝘮𝘦.𝘕𝘰𝘸 everywhere – It might break your app (and your brain)Many C# devs use DateTime.Now without a second thought.But here's the thing — DateTime.Now is local time, and that can be a trap in modern apps.𝐖𝐡𝐲 𝐢𝐭 𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐬:- Your app might run on multiple servers across time zones- Local time shifts with Daylight Saving Time- Comparing DateTime.Now values between systems? Risky business𝐔𝐬𝐞 𝐔𝐭𝐜𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐢𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐚𝐝:- Perfect for logging, storing timestamps, and calculating durationsI learned this the hard way while debugging user session expiries — all because DateTime.Now jumped an hour forward.𝘗𝘳𝘰 𝘛𝘪𝘱:Store in UTC, convert to local only when displaying to the user.How about you?Do you default to UtcNow in your code? Or do you still use Now in certain cases? Let’s discuss! 👇♻️ Repost and follow Umer Farooq for more .NET tips!hashtag#dotnet hashtag#csharp

1️⃣- ال Hangfire تعتبر Open Source Library في Dot NET من خلاله نقدر ننفذ Background Jobs من غير lock ال main- thread  اللى شغال و بتوفر ليك Dashboard من خلاله تقدر تتابع Tasks من حيث jobs بتكون Enqueue و Process و schedule و Success و await و Recurring  . 2️⃣- من أهم مميزاته سهل الدمج مع أي Data Source .3️⃣- انواع ال Jobs  و executed ازي ..؟ 📍- Fire-and-Forget Jobs( تتنفذ مره واحد فقط )BackgroundJob.Enqueue(()=>Console.WriteLine("Hangfire only one time");📍- Delayed Jobs ( تنفذه في وقت انت محدده)BackgroundJob.Schedule(() => Console.WriteLine("This job runs after 10 minutes"), TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10));📍- Recurring Jobs ( تكرر تنفذه )RecurringJob.AddOrUpdate("my-recurring-job", () => Console.WriteLine("Runs every minute"), Cron.Minutely);📑و اهم المقالات اللى تفهم منها : 📍 Medium: https://lnkd.in/dxW-VZJH.📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/d44VRaw4📽️ و اهم الفيديوهات اللى تفهم منها : 📍DevCreed: https://lnkd.in/dPiCzeGd📍 Milan Jovanovie : https://lnkd.in/dypRaV-5📍 Code Maze : https://lnkd.in/dHkTmqZShashtag#dotnet hashtag#backend hashtag#frontend hashtag#CSharp hashtag#HangFire hashtag#Async hashtag#Developers hashtag#Jobs hashtag#Delay hashtag#rajab

Stop using 𝘋𝘢𝘵𝘦𝘛𝘪𝘮𝘦.𝘕𝘰𝘸 everywhere – It might break your app (and your brain)Many C# devs use DateTime.Now without a second thought.But here's the thing — DateTime.Now is local time, and that can be a trap in modern apps.𝐖𝐡𝐲 𝐢𝐭 𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐬:- Your app might run on multiple servers across time zones- Local time shifts with Daylight Saving Time- Comparing DateTime.Now values between systems? Risky business𝐔𝐬𝐞 𝐔𝐭𝐜𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐢𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐚𝐝:- Perfect for logging, storing timestamps, and calculating durationsI learned this the hard way while debugging user session expiries — all because DateTime.Now jumped an hour forward.𝘗𝘳𝘰 𝘛𝘪𝘱:Store in UTC, convert to local only when displaying to the user.How about you?Do you default to UtcNow in your code? Or do you still use Now in certain cases? Let’s discuss! 👇♻️ Repost and follow Umer Farooq for more .NET tips!hashtag#dotnet hashtag#csharp
